energy.usef.agr.model

Class VariationRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • energy.usef.agr.model.DeviceRequest
      • energy.usef.agr.model.VariationRequest
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    IncreaseRequest, ReduceRequest

    @MappedSuperclass
public abstract class VariationRequest
extends DeviceRequest
    Abstract class child of DeviceRequest. A VariationRequest can either be a request to reduce the power for a certain duration or increase the power for a certain duration (both durations given by a Start DTU and a End DTU).
